title: Drax Project - Complete Discography - 320kbps
description:
******
About:
******
 Drax Project are a four piece band from Wellington, New Zealand. They started 
 out doing late night busking sessions in the City - creating their own unique 
 versions of hip-hop and pop tracks. After entertaining crowds of hundreds on 
 the street, they began using what they'd learned, and earned, on writing and 
 recording original music. Their debut EP was well received, ultimately 
 resulting in their signing to Universal. While still known for their killer 
 live remixes - the boys have been working hard to produce studio records that 
 reflect where they want to take their sound.

*****
Band:
*****
 Shaan Singh - Saxophone | Lead Vocals | Synth
 Matt Beachen - Drums
 Sam Thomson - Bass | Synth | Vocals
 Ben O'Leary - Guitar | Vocals
